questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where payment transactions are failing to rollback during partial failures in a parallel processing batch. The application uses Spring Boot with Hibernate, and the service is defined as follows:

java
@Service
public class PaymentService {
    @Autowired
    private PaymentRepository repo;

    public void processPaymentBatch(List<Payment> payments) {
        payments.parallelStream().forEach(this::savePayment);
    }

    @Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)
    public void savePayment(Payment payment) {
        repo.save(payment);
        if (payment.getAmount() < 0) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Invalid amount");
        }
    }
}
